02:38.050 --> 02:42.300
<i>These animals don't listen
No, not one little bit</i>

02:42.420 --> 02:46.380
<i>They run around out of control
And throw their hissy fits</i>

02:46.520 --> 02:50.170
<i>It's up to me to stop them
'Cause plainly you can see</i>

02:50.320 --> 02:53.120
<i>It's got to be my destiny</i>

02:53.270 --> 02:56.050
<i>And it's what
My cutie mark is telling me</i>

02:59.370 --> 03:03.430
