Oh my, what a terrible dream I had.

11:54.720 --> 11:56.640
Or, maybe I'm still having it.

11:56.760 --> 11:59.580
Rarity, Pinkie Pie is about
to lose the apple farm.

11:59.700 --> 12:01.100
We need Applejack's help!

12:01.220 --> 12:03.080
Lose the apple farm?

12:03.180 --> 12:05.110
Well we can't let that happen,
now can we?

12:05.420 --> 12:08.750
