<i>A mark of one's destiny,
singled out alone, fulfilled.</i>

13:40.810 --> 13:42.320
Wait a second, that's it!

13:42.440 --> 13:45.260
I understand now,
I know how to fix the spell!

13:50.190 --> 13:53.430
From all of us together,
together we are friends,

13:53.550 --> 13:57.460
with the marks of our destinies made one,
there is magic without end!

14:21.320 --> 14:22.910
What happened?

14:36.490 --> 14:41.220
Hello? Where am I?
What is this place?

14:44.880 --> 14:48.860
Congratulations, Twilight.
I knew you could do it.

14:48.980 --> 14:52.890
Princess! I don't understand.
What did I do?

14:53.010 --> 14:56.250
You did something today
that's never been done before.

14:56.370 --> 15:01.570
Something even a great unicorn like
Star Swirl the Bearded was not able to do.

15:01.690 --> 15:05.460
Because he did not understand
friendship like you do.

15:05.580 --> 15:09.750
The lessons you've learned here in Ponyville
have taught you well.

15:09.860 --> 15:12.820
You have proven that you're ready,
Twilight.

15:12.940 --> 15:15.920
Ready? Ready for what?

15:22.600 --> 15:28.570
<i>You've come such a long, long way</i>

15:28.570 --> 15:33.980
<i>And I've watched you
From that very first day</i>

15:34.100 --> 15:37.180
<i>To see how you might grow</i>

15:37.400 --> 15:39.740
<i>To see what you might do</i>

15:40.660 --> 15:42.490
<i>To see what you've been through</i>

15:42.570 --> 15:48.250
<i>And all the ways
You've made me proud of you</i>

15:52.420 --> 15:57.970
<i>It's time now
For a new change to come</i>

15:58.090 --> 16:04.560
<i>You've grown up
And your new life has begun</i>

16:04.680 --> 16:07.180
<i>To go where you will go</i>

16:07.300 --> 16:10.440
<i>To see what you will see</i>

16:10.560 --> 16:12.480
<i>To find what you will be</i>

16:12.600 --> 16:15.520
<i>For it's time for you</i>

16:15.640 --> 16:21.910
<i>To fulfill your destiny</i>

16:49.550 --> 16:52.480
Twilight...? Is that you?

16:59.710 --> 17:02.320
I... I've never seen
anything like it!

17:02.760 --> 17:05.590
Twilight's got wings! Awesome!

17:05.710 --> 17:07.950
A new flying buddy!

17:08.100 --> 17:12.240
Why, you've become an alicorn.
I didn't even know that was possible.

17:12.360 --> 17:14.820
Alicorn party!

17:17.670 --> 17:21.290
Wow... you look just like a princess!

17:21.410 --> 17:24.470
That's because she is a princess.

17:26.490 --> 17:28.460
Hold on a second!

17:33.740 --> 17:35.990
A princess?

17:36.440 --> 17:38.250
Since you've come to Ponyville,

17:38.370 --> 17:44.410
you've displayed the charity, compassion,
devotion, integrity, optimism,

17:44.530 --> 17:48.290
and of course,
the leadership of a true princess.

17:48.410 --> 17:51.370
But... does this mean
I won't be your student anymore?

17:51.490 --> 17:53.550
Not in the same way as before.

17:53.670 --> 17:58.700
I'll still be here to help and guide you,
but we're all your students now, too.

17:59.350 --> 18:03.140
You are an inspiration to us all,
Twilight.

18:06.510 --> 18:08.810
But... what do I do now?

18:08.940 --> 18:11.700
Is there a book about
being a princess I should read?

18:12.420 --> 18:15.520
There will be time
for all of that later.

18:23.840 --> 18:28.070
We are gathered here today
in celebration of a momentous occasion.

18:28.190 --> 18:31.480
My most faithful student,
Twilight Sparkle,

18:31.600 --> 18:35.470
has done many extraordinary things
since she's lived in Ponyville.

18:35.590 --> 18:40.420
She even helped reunite me
with my sister, Princess Luna.

18:40.540 --> 18:44.430
But today, Twilight Sparkle
did something extraordinary.

18:44.820 --> 18:47.500
She created new magic,

18:47.620 --> 18:50.060
proving without a doubt
that she is ready

18:50.060 --> 18:53.620
to be crowned
Equestria's newest princess.

18:54.040 --> 18:59.910
Fillies and gentlecolts,
may I present for the very first time,

18:59.910 --> 19:02.240
Princess Twilight Sparkle!

19:02.640 --> 19:05.910
<i>Thou Princess Twilight cometh</i>

19:06.060 --> 19:09.430
<i>Behold, behold</i>

19:09.550 --> 19:12.420
<i>A Princess here before us</i>

19:12.540 --> 19:19.340
<i>Behold, behold, behold</i>

19:19.460 --> 19:23.250
<i>Behold, behold
(behold, behold)</i>

19:23.370 --> 19:25.630
<i>The Princess Twilight cometh</i>

19:26.090 --> 19:30.300
<i>Behold, behold
(behold, behold)</i>

19:30.420 --> 19:33.210
<i>The Princess is
(the Princess is)</i>

19:33.210 --> 19:36.330
<i>Here!</i>

19:40.040 --> 19:42.120
Say something, Princess.

19:44.370 --> 19:45.890
A little while ago,

19:46.010 --> 19:50.300
my teacher and mentor Princess Celestia
sent me to live in Ponyville.

19:50.420 --> 19:52.760
She sent me to study friendship,

19:52.880 --> 19:56.220
which is something
I didn't really care much about.

19:56.340 --> 20:00.810
But now, on a day like today,
I can honestly say

20:00.930 --> 20:03.090
I wouldn't be standing here
if it weren't for the friendships

20:03.210 --> 20:05.220
I've made with all of you.

20:05.340 --> 20:09.190
Each one of you taught me something
about friendship, and for that,

20:09.310 --> 20:11.520
I will always be grateful.

20:11.640 --> 20:16.130
